gemini.title: Gemini
gemini.description: Gemini is an AI-powered financial platform offering cryptocurrency exchange and custody services. It enables users to trade, store, and manage various cryptocurrencies.

chatgpt.title: ChatGPT
chatgpt.description: ChatGPT is an AI language model developed by OpenAI, capable of generating human-like text responses in natural language conversations. It can answer queries and engage in conversation on various topics.

midjourney.title: Midjourney
midjourney.description: Midjourney is an AI-driven platform specializing in image generation. It uses advanced machine learning algorithms to create realistic images based on user inputs or preferences.

openai.title: OpenAI
openai.description: OpenAI is an artificial intelligence research lab dedicated to advancing AI capabilities in a safe and beneficial manner. It has developed various AI models, including ChatGPT, to address diverse applications.

google-ai.title: Google AI
google-ai.description: Google AI encompasses a wide range of research and development efforts by Google in the field of artificial intelligence. It includes projects such as Google Brain, Google Assistant, and TensorFlow.
